OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,FAn inquiry scrutinising the events
OL,7,Fleading up to the Nottingham attacks
OL,8,Fin which three people were killed by a
OL,9,Fschizophrenic man will examine the
OL,10,Fconcerns of bereaved families and
OL,11,Fsurvivors who have gone through
OL,12,F"personal tragedy", it has heard.
OL,14,FValdo Calocane, who had been diagnosed
OL,15,Fwith paranoid schizophrenia, killed
OL,16,FUniversity of Nottingham students
OL,17,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,18,FKumar, both 19, and caretaker Ian
OL,19,FCoates, 65, and attempted to kill
OL,20,Fthree more people in Nottingham in
OL,21,FJune 2023.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,FProsecutors, police and medical
OL,7,Fprofessionals will be scrutinised by
OL,8,Fthe two-year public inquiry, chaired
OL,9,Fby retired senior judge Deborah
OL,10,FTaylor, which is expected to hear from
OL,11,Fmore than 100 witnesses.
OL,13,FIn her opening statement on Monday,
OL,14,Fcounsel to the inquiry, Rachel
OL,15,FLangdale KC, outlined concerns about
OL,16,FCalocane's case, who is referred to as
OL,17,FVC in the inquiry, which will be
OL,18,Fexamined.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,FShe said: "Whilst we refer to the
OL,7,FNottingham attacks collectively, each
OL,8,Fattack was on an individual, and each
OL,9,Fattack is a personal tragedy for the
OL,10,Fvictims, their families, and those
OL,11,Fclose to them."
OL,13,FMs Langdale continued: "The inquiry
OL,14,Fcan and will examine the underlying
OL,15,Ffactual material in the case of VC,
OL,16,Frelating to the psychiatric evidence
OL,17,Fobtained for the sentencing hearing
OL,18,Fand whether or not all factual
OL,19,Finformation now known was known at the
OL,20,Ftime.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@OO]uD@XOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,F"The inquiry is able to examine other
OL,7,Fconcerns of the bereaved families and
OL,8,Fsurvivors, including the adequacy of
OL,9,Fthe response of the police when VC was
OL,10,Fin custody following the attacks, and
OL,11,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service's
OL,12,Fhandling of the case.
OL,14,F"What was the procedure employed and
OL,15,Fbasis of decisions taken as to VC's
OL,16,Ffitness to be interviewed and
OL,17,Fdetention? What strategy and
OL,18,Fprocedures were followed for
OL,19,Ftoxicology?
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,F"Were attempts made to take samples,
OL,7,Fand should further investigations have
OL,8,Fbeen carried out, how did the police
OL,9,Fhandle communications with other
OL,10,Fagencies, the media, and the bereaved
OL,11,Ffamilies and survivors of the attacks?
OL,13,F"Covid restrictions were relevant when
OL,14,FCalocane had several medical
OL,15,Fappointments, and the inquiry will
OL,16,Falso explore whether and how they
OL,17,Fimpacted, Ms Langdale said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,7,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,8,F2024 after admitting manslaughter by
OL,9,Fdiminished responsibility and
OL,10,Fattempted murder ` something which has
OL,11,Fbeen widely criticised by the victims'
OL,12,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,FMs Langdale told the inquiry that "key
OL,7,Fthemes" emerge from reports that have
OL,8,Falready been undertaken in relation to
OL,9,FCalocane and his mental health care,
OL,10,Fincluding a Care Quality Commission
OL,11,F(CQC) report, which found that the
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust (NHFT) made errors,
OL,14,Fsuch as discharging him to his GP in
OL,15,F2022.
OL,26,@nD@cOUoD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,FShe said: "We suggest some key themes
OL,7,Femerge from these investigations and
OL,8,Freports, and whether described
OL,9,Fcurrently as learning points, failings
OL,10,For criticisms, they provide a baseline
OL,11,Fcritique upon which we will build.
OL,13,F"The approach to risk assessment, the
OL,14,Fdynamic nature of risk, and the need
OL,15,Fto have a clear and accurate history
OL,16,Fare all key themes.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,F"When should the risk VC presented in
OL,7,Fthe community have been recognised and
OL,8,Fwhat should have been done about it?
OL,9,FWas there any attempt to reduce the
OL,10,Frisk? Was there any attempt at
OL,11,Fassertive outreach? If not, why not?
OL,13,F"Whilst depot medication, a long-
OL,14,Flasting injection of medication, was
OL,15,Fconsidered in relation to VC's non-
OL,16,Fconcordance, it was never instituted.
OL,17,FVC's antipathy towards it was given
OL,18,Fpriority over its benefits in risk
OL,19,Fmanagement.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,F"This, and the failure to consider
OL,7,Fdepot medication as a condition of a
OL,8,Fcommunity treatment order on discharge
OL,9,Ffrom VC's third admission, will be
OL,10,Fexamined in detail."
OL,12,FThe CQC report said Calocane's records
OL,13,Fmake it "clear" that he was "acutely
OL,14,Funwell" throughout the two years he
OL,15,Fwas under the care of NHFT.
OL,17,FHe was psychotic and suffering from
OL,18,Fparanoid delusions before eventually
OL,19,Fbeing diagnosed with paranoid
OL,20,Fschizophrenia in July 2020.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]uD@IOUuD@OO]uD@]OUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,FThe regulator had said that while some
OL,7,Frisks were highlighted, other
OL,8,Fassessments "minimised or omitted key
OL,9,Fdetails".
OL,11,FThese include the fact that Calocane
OL,12,Frefused to take his medication, had
OL,13,Fongoing and persistent symptoms of
OL,14,Fpsychosis, was violent to others when
OL,15,Fpsychosis was not managed well, and
OL,16,Fescalated his violent behaviour in the
OL,17,Flater stages of his care.
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1771952662
OL,3,CInquiry will have families at centre
OL,4,Cof Nottingham attacks concerns examined
OL,6,FMs Langdale said the inquiry, which
OL,7,Fincludes more than 60 statements from
OL,8,Fpolice and 169 statements from the
OL,9,Fmental health trust which cared for
OL,10,FCalocane, will take a "holistic
OL,11,Fapproach" to examining the case.
OL,13,FThe chairwoman of the inquiry will be
OL,14,Frequired to produce a report and
OL,15,Fprovide recommendations by May 2027,
OL,16,F"so that lessons can be learned to
OL,17,Fprevent similar attacks in the
OL,18,Ffuture", Ms Langdale said.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@IO]xD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
